This also looks a bit wrong:
> > +	if (vt) {
> > +		/*
> > +		 * If we raced with con_close(), `vt' may be null.
> > +		 * Hence this bandaid.   - akpm
> > +		 */
> > +		acquire_console_sem();
> > +		set_cursor(vt->vc_num);
> > +		release_console_sem();
> > +	}
Maybe should be:
acquire_console_sem();
if (vt) set_cursor(vt->vc_num);
release_console_sem();
??
